This is a README file of SALB.


This repository contain the source code of PVFS2 with the SALB algorithm.
All source codes and documents in this repository are only used for academic exchanges, not for commercial activities.


To compile PVFS2 with SALB algorithm, you need to install GNU Scientific Library development package
For example, on a Debian distribution, you can use: apt-get install libgsl0-dev 
For the README file of PVFS2, you can read README.PVFS2

More documentations is under development.
However, you can find some details of SALB in PVFS2 in our paper:

Bin Dong, Xiuqiao Li, Limin Xiao, Li Ruan, and Binbin Yu. 2010. Self-Acting Load Balancing with Parallel Sub File Migration for Parallel File System. In Proceedings of the 2010 Third International Joint Conference on Computational Science and Optimization - Volume 02 (CSO '10), Vol. 2. IEEE Computer Society, Washington, DC, USA, 317-321. 

Any questions, you can contact
Bin Dong at goon83@126.com or Bondg@cse.buaa.edu.cn

